◆ IO_PinGet()

STD_PIN_STATE_e IO_PinGet ( const volatile uint32_t *  pRegisterAddress,
uint32_t  pin 
)

Get pin state.

The TMS570LC43 has only few dedicated GPIO register. Most of the time the IOs are controlled by a dedicated register in the corresponding peripheral.

Parameters
pRegisterAddressaddress of pin output register
pinbit position corresponding to pin in register
Returns
STD_PIN_STATE_e state of the pin
